'''Yuba''' iga yan unazur d umdyaz amaziɣ s taclhit n sus, yan ɣ inazurn li syatuyn azawan amaziɣ igas atig. Yuba iga yan ɣ inaẓurn lli s yattun ammussu nu tusna tamaziɣt. Iwaliwn tasfififinns ar sawal f ufgan d wakal d tudrtnsn

== Assaɣ ==
Assaɣns amzwaru Musa Habbun, ɣ tudrt n umdyas is assaɣ n yuba li igan assaɣ ni yan ɣ igllidn n tamurt n tamzɣa.

==Talult d tudertn ɣ mẓẓi== 

Ilul ɣ 1968 ɣ [[Dcayra]], yat yan uduwar mqqurn gr Ugadir d [[inzggan]] ɣ tama n iɣrm n Ugadir. ḍin nit aɣ iẓri mẓẓi nns wala tiɣrins. Idda yuba, immli ɣ tmazirt nns wali tin wiyyad aylli yas ikfan yan usmmaql yadnin i tudrt.

==Tudrtn n unazur==

Lliɣ n imqqur s imik, ittut zund kigan n ayt tmazirtns s usurs amazdar n idlsns, idls amaziɣ. Mkan af yusi afrak ar isiggil man taɣarast as rad yaws ɣ ussfrkns, immaɣ f tussna tunsîbt s uğug ad amzwaru n tmagit tanamurt n Lmrruk. Issnti ar ittara amarg s tmaziɣt afa d iml tayrins i idls ad, urta iga azêmmazlns izwarn ɣ ubaraz n uzawan.

Ifls mas iga uzawan yan imis isugrn ɣ ubrid n tamaɣt, isnti ar ikkit idinann n tgitart yaws ɣ tlalit n yat trabbut n umarg. Mqqar fllasn tqqn tnbâdt abrid n isuyas, iɣi Yuba ad iskr mnnaw imddrzn ɣ kigan d tmdinin n Mrruk ississan anaw n umargns gr tuggt n imarayn n umarg amaziɣ. Azawanns ard ittagwm ɣ idlsns azayku, ɣ usala ns idran, mac Yuba ihâbbl tarmiwin n wiyyâd, ihîyl i inmuggar d idlsan n umadâl. Snat tsffifin lli d idî Yuba ar mmalant tafssa ns f ad isflujju amarg issackid iwaliwn isnmili azawan.

==Tamdyazt d imasn nu amarg==
Ɣ 2000, tasffiftns izwarn tawargit lli yura, iga s tiyt, yirirt tssen aɣaras s ulawn ggutnin ɣ Mrruk. Ɣ 2005 issufɣ d tis snat ngr Mrruk d Uliman ig as Itran Azal nttat aɣ isatig imasn iqburn n darsn zund lutar, ahjhuj, amzâd (rribab), ganga, tallunt, tiqrqawin, nnaqus d wiyyâd. Asml tudrt ad imla yaɣ  yan Yuba yadnin, Yuba izêdârn ad if tudrt yadnin i imasn imaziɣn imzwura, amzâd nɣ rribab lli ilan aɣ ar yan udinan, iggammi ad lli an izri igran n Sus, igwdl f imzgan ur isslfldn i tamaziɣt. Yuba imla rribab i willi t ur issn, tasffift igwran n Yuba tga tamɣra ngr imassn n idls [[amaziɣ]] d imasn n umadâl. S tugga n mnnaw infran, amarg n umdyazn nɣ aàzri ikkisd amarg amaziɣ n rways d win uhêwac ɣ tfulklurit d tatut isls as timlsit tamaynut igt d isli ngr izawann n wiyyaḍ.

== Azawan d tamagit ==
Asml urt igi iktr s taɣlaɣalt n tagnawit, amarg n tgnawit yusin tabratt urd tagnawit aɣar i tgnawit, ɣ wanaw ad ɣ uzawan Yuba issimɣur willi izzîdêrn i tissumga ''« isggurad ufgan tissumga, idîd assudn ufus d ays ntbndaq, d ays nttini sidi mqart ur igi».''
